Constructor Detail

LaunchTransform

public LaunchTransform(java.lang.String path,
                       java.lang.String pathType)
The path may be an IResource to a file in the workspace, or an IPath to a file outside of the workspace - depending on the pathType. The path should be created using IPath.toPortableString(). The path may also contain variables defined by the VariablePlugin.
